@wp.kernel
def expr_kowefa(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.07)) * 0.11)
    v0 = wp.exp(v2)
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.78 * v0 + 0.67)) + v0)
    data[tid] = v0
